o the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" is also to present a grain offering of two quarts "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit a tenth (of an ephah)"},{"kind":"text","text":" of fine flour mixed with a quart "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit a fourth hin, also in v. 5"},{"kind":"text","text":" of oil. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit a tenth (of an ephah)"},{"marker":2,"text":"Lit a fourth hin, also in v. 5"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Prepare a quart of wine as a drink offering "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 29:40","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":40,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:13","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" with the burnt offering or sacrifice of each lamb."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 29:40","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":40},{"label":"Lv 23:13","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“If you prepare a grain offering with a ram, it is to be four quarts "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit two-tenths (of an ephah)"},{"kind":"text","text":" of fine flour mixed with a third of a gallon "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit a third hin, also in v. 7"},{"kind":"text","text":" of oil. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:13","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 28:9","book":"Num","chapter":28,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 28:12","book":"Num","chapter":28,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 23:13","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":13},{"label":"Nm 28:9","book":"Num","chapter":28,"verse":9},{"label":"Nm 28:12","book":"Num","chapter":28,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit two-tenths (of an ephah)"},{"marker":2,"text":"Lit a third hin, also in v. 7"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Also present a third of a gallon of wine for a drink offering as a pleasing aroma to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“If you prepare a young bull as a burnt offering or as a sacrifice, to fulfill a vow, or as a fellowship offering to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"a grain offering of six quarts "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit three-tenths (of an ephah)"},{"kind":"text","text":" of fine flour mixed with two quarts "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit a half hin, also in v. 10"},{"kind":"text","text":" of oil is to be presented with the bull. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 28:12","book":"Num","chapter":28,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 28:12","book":"Num","chapter":28,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit three-tenths (of an ephah)"},{"marker":2,"text":"Lit a half hin, also in v. 10"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Also present two quarts of wine as a drink offering. It is a food offering, a pleasing aroma to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is to be done for each ox, ram, lamb, or goat. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is how you are to prepare each of them, no matter how many."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Every Israelite is to prepare these things in this way when he presents a food offering as a pleasing aroma to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When an alien resides with you or someone else is among you and wants to prepare a food offering as a pleasing aroma to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", he is to do exactly as you do throughout your generations. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The assembly is to have the same statute for both you and the resident alien as a permanent statute throughout your generations. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 27:21","book":"Exo","chapter":27,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 3:17","book":"Lev","chapter":3,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 7:36","book":"Lev","chapter":7,"verse":36,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 10:9","book":"Lev","chapter":10,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:14","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":14,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:31","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":31,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 23:41","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":41,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 24:3","book":"Lev","chapter":24,"verse":3,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 10:8","book":"Num","chapter":10,"verse":8,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 18:23","book":"Num","chapter":18,"verse":23,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" You and the alien will be alike before the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 27:21","book":"Exo","chapter":27,"verse":21},{"label":"Lv 3:17","book":"Lev","chapter":3,"verse":17},{"label":"Lv 7:36","book":"Lev","chapter":7,"verse":36},{"label":"Lv 10:9","book":"Lev","chapter":10,"verse":9},{"label":"Lv 23:14","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":14},{"label":"Lv 23:31","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":31},{"label":"Lv 23:41","book":"Lev","chapter":23,"verse":41},{"label":"Lv 24:3","book":"Lev","chapter":24,"verse":3},{"label":"Nm 10:8","book":"Num","chapter":10,"verse":8},{"label":"Nm 18:23","book":"Num","chapter":18,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The same law and the same ordinance will apply to both you and the alien who resides with you.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 12:19","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 12:49","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":49,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 16:29","book":"Lev","chapter":16,"verse":29,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 17:8–16","book":"Lev","chapter":17,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 9:14","book":"Num","chapter":9,"verse":14,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 15:26","book":"Num","chapter":15,"verse":26,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 15:29","book":"Num","chapter":15,"verse":29,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 19:10","book":"Num","chapter":19,"verse":10,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 35:15","book":"Num","chapter":35,"verse":15,"letter":"i"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 12:19","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":19},{"label":"Ex 12:49","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":49},{"label":"Lv 16:29","book":"Lev","chapter":16,"verse":29},{"label":"Lv 17:8–16","book":"Lev","chapter":17,"verse":8},{"label":"Nm 9:14","book":"Num","chapter":9,"verse":14},{"label":"Nm 15:26","book":"Num","chapter":15,"verse":26},{"label":"Nm 15:29","book":"Num","chapter":15,"verse":29},{"label":"Nm 19:10","book":"Num","chapter":19,"verse":10},{"label":"Nm 35:15","book":"Num","chapter":35,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" instructed Moses, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Speak to the Israelites and tell them: After you enter the land where I am bringing you, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"you are to offer a contribution to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" when you eat from the food of the land. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You are to offer a loaf from your first batch of dough "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 10:37","book":"Neh","chapter":10,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 44:30","book":"Ezk","chapter":44,"verse":30,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" as a contribution; offer it just like a contribution from the threshing floor. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 2:14","book":"Lev","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Neh 10:37","book":"Neh","chapter":10,"verse":37},{"label":"Ezk 44:30","book":"Ezk","chapter":44,"verse":30},{"label":"Lv 2:14","book":"Lev","chapter":2,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Throughout your generations, you are to give the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" a contribution from the first batch of your dough."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“When you sin unintentionally and do not obey all these commands that the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" spoke to Moses "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 4:2","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 4:2","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"all that the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" has commanded you through Moses, from the day the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" issued the commands and onward throughout your generations — "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and if it was done unintentionally without the community’s awareness, the entire community is to prepare one young bull for a burnt offering as a pleasing aroma to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", with its grain offering and drink offering according to the regulation, and one male goat as a sin offering. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The priest will then make atonement for the entire Israelite community so that they may be forgiven, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 4:20","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 4:26","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 4:31","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":31,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 4:35","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":35,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 19:20","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":20,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 5:1","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":1,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the sin was unintentional. They are to bring their offering, a food offering to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", and their sin offering before the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" for their unintentional sin. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 4:20","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":20},{"label":"Lv 4:26","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":26},{"label":"Lv 4:31","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":31},{"label":"Lv 4:35","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":35},{"label":"Lv 19:20","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":20},{"label":"Jr 5:1","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The entire Israelite community and the alien who resides among them will be forgiven, since it happened to all the people unintentionally."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“If one person sins unintentionally, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 4:27","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":27,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" he is to present a year-old female goat as a sin offering. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 4:27","book":"Lev","chapter":4,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The priest will then make atonement before the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" on behalf of the person who acts in error sinning unintentionally, and when he makes atonement for him, he will be forgiven. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You are to have the same law for the person who acts in error, whether he is an Israelite or an alien who resides among you."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“But the person who acts defiantly, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit with a high hand"},{"kind":"text","text":" whether native or resident alien, blasphemes the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 19:6","book":"2Ki","chapter":19,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 19:22","book":"2Ki","chapter":19,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 37:6","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 37:23","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":23,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 20:27","book":"Ezk","chapter":20,"verse":27,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" That person is to be cut off from his people. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 19:6","book":"2Ki","chapter":19,"verse":6},{"label":"2Kg 19:22","book":"2Ki","chapter":19,"verse":22},{"label":"Is 37:6","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":6},{"label":"Is 37:23","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":23},{"label":"Ezk 20:27","book":"Ezk","chapter":20,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit with a high hand"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He will certainly be cut off, because he has despised the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s word and broken his command; his guilt remains on him.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"While the Israelites were in the wilderness, they found a man gathering wood on the Sabbath day. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 35:2–3","book":"Exo","chapter":35,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 35:2–3","book":"Exo","chapter":35,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Those who found him gathering wood brought him to Moses, Aaron, and the entire community. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They placed him in custody because it had not been decided what should be done to him. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:35","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" told Moses, “The man is to be put to death. The entire community is to stone him outside the camp.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 20:27","book":"Lev","chapter":20,"verse":27,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 24:14","book":"Lev","chapter":24,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 24:23","book":"Lev","chapter":24,"verse":23,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 14:10","book":"Num","chapter":14,"verse":10,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 7:25","book":"Jos","chapter":7,"verse":25,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 16:40","book":"Ezk","chapter":16,"verse":40,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 21:35","book":"Mat","chapter":21,"verse":35,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 14:19","book":"Act","chapter":14,"verse":19,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 11:25","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":25,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:37","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":37,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 12:20","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":20,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 20:27","book":"Lev","chapter":20,"verse":27},{"label":"Lv 24:14","book":"Lev","chapter":24,"verse":14},{"label":"Lv 24:23","book":"Lev","chapter":24,"verse":23},{"label":"Nm 14:10","book":"Num","chapter":14,"verse":10},{"label":"Jos 7:25","book":"Jos","chapter":7,"verse":25},{"label":"Ezk 16:40","book":"Ezk","chapter":16,"verse":40},{"label":"Mt 21:35","book":"Mat","chapter":21,"verse":35},{"label":"Ac 14:19","book":"Act","chapter":14,"verse":19},{"label":"2Co 11:25","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":25},{"label":"Heb 11:37","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":37},{"label":"Heb 12:20","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:36","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So the entire community brought him outside the camp and stoned him to death, as the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" had commanded Moses."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:37","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" said to Moses, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:38","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Speak to the Israelites and tell them that throughout their generations they are to make tassels "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 22:12","book":"Deu","chapter":22,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 9:20","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 14:36","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":36,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 23:5","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the corners of their garments, and put a blue cord on the tassel at each corner. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 22:12","book":"Deu","chapter":22,"verse":12},{"label":"Mt 9:20","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":20},{"label":"Mt 14:36","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":36},{"label":"Mt 23:5","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:39","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These will serve as tassels for you to look at, so that you may remember all the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s commands and obey them and not prostitute yourselves by following your own heart "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 3:17","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 9:14","book":"Jer","chapter":9,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 16:12","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 18:12","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 14:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":14,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 20:16","book":"Ezk","chapter":20,"verse":16,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 33:31","book":"Ezk","chapter":33,"verse":31,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" and your own eyes. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 31:7","book":"Job","chapter":31,"verse":7,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 3:17","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":17},{"label":"Jr 9:14","book":"Jer","chapter":9,"verse":14},{"label":"Jr 16:12","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":12},{"label":"Jr 18:12","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":12},{"label":"Ezk 14:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":14,"verse":7},{"label":"Ezk 20:16","book":"Ezk","chapter":20,"verse":16},{"label":"Ezk 33:31","book":"Ezk","chapter":33,"verse":31},{"label":"Jb 31:7","book":"Job","chapter":31,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:40","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This way you will remember and obey all my commands and be holy to your God. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:15:41","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God who brought you out of the land of Egypt to be your God; I am the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 29:46","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":46,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 19:36","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":36,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 25:38","book":"Lev","chapter":25,"verse":38,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 26:13","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":13,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 29:46","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":46},{"label":"Lv 19:36","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":36},{"label":"Lv 25:38","book":"Lev","chapter":25,"verse":38},{"label":"Lv 26:13","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279345670}